                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A bishop\u2019s eerie, fishlike appearance evokes feelings of unsettling fear in foes within a 30-foot radius. The bishop can use this aura as a free action, and any creature within this area must succeed at a DC 16 Will save or become shaken for 5d6 rounds. A creature that succeeds at its save is immune to the bishop\u2019s aura for 24 hours. The save DC is Wisdom-based."
